This paper is about using TextRank for information retrieval, which falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also deals with natural language processing (NLP) techniques such as sentence and paragraph-level analysis, which falls under the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). The use of TextRank also involves machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper deals with graph-based algorithms, which falls under the category of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS).
